   <a href=http://pub51.ezboard.com/flightoftherealmfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=57.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The new rates</span><hr size=1> Well I still consider the price to be worth it.  And I have to assume that their research indicates that so do most players.  Remember EQ is a bushiness to these people.  Like any bushiness venture they want to make as much money with it as possible.  Remember that they are providing you with a service, and you can't expect them to do that without making it worth their while.  I hope that their increased profits will provide more capitol to put back into the game to make it a better product.  Thus attracting more customer further increasing profits (see the cycle here).  Basically you have have to decide whether or not EQ is worth the new price.  If it is pay the new rate and continue to enjoy the game.  If it is not don't pay and stop playing.  If enough people decide that it is not then Sony will have to decide whether they should reduce the price or discontinue the product.   <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub51.ezboard.com/utelpierion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Telpierion</A> at: 3/27/02 1:32:12 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub51.ezboard.com/uarkkana.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arkkana</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/27/02 9:36:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub51.ezboard.com/flightoftherealmfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=57.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The new rates</span><hr size=1> Geez! Telp went right to the point of things there.  Nonetheless, I have to agree with her statement.  EQ/Verant is a business and therefore, in order to stay on top, they must risk doing certain things that will/might/could hurt some people but make it worth somewhere down the road.<br><br>3 extra bucks is not much for the average consumer.  Sure, there goes the happy meal for college kids, or there goes that gas money you saved up.  But if you like the game and like the people that you have made great friends with then 3 dollars is worth it.<br><br>And remember, we should be lucky that we are paying this much a month and not paying 40 bucks to play this game <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub51.ezboard.com/ujunica.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Junica</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Goddess Of All That Is Light</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/27/02 7:19:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub51.ezboard.com/flightoftherealmfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=57.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The new rates</span><hr size=1> Don't get me started on my internet bill....but you all are well worth it!<br><br>/hugs <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub51.ezboard.com/flightoftherealmfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=57.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub51.ezboard.com/flightoftherealmfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=57.topic&index=4><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub51.ezboard.com/flightoftherealmfrm1.threadControl?topicID=57.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a>